Import apps and packages:
- `apps/app` main frontend app
- `apps/api` backend api and workflows
- `packages/design-system` reusable design system components
- `packages/domain` core domain models, used by the backend and the frontend
- `packages/queries` shared useQuery hooks
- `packages/database` database schema and migrations
- `packages/tailwind-config` shared global tailwind config